#: speech:1
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are becoming angry."
msgstr "Tus criaturas se están volviendo irritables."

#: speech:2
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are angry - they have nowhere to live."
msgstr "Tus criaturas están irritadas, no tienen donde vivir."

#: speech:3
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your minions are annoyed - you cannot pay them."
msgstr "Tus servidores están perplejos, no puedes pagarles."

#: speech:4
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are upset because they are hungry."
msgstr "Tus criaturas están alteradas porque están hambrientas."

#: speech:5
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your minions are vandalizing your dungeon!"
msgstr "¡Tus servidores están saqueando tu mazmorra!"

#: speech:6
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Creatures are deserting!"
msgstr "¡Las criaturas están desertando!"

#: speech:7
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The enemy has broken through your walls!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo ha irrumpido a través de los muros!"

#: speech:8
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Dungeon Heart is being attacked!"
msgstr "¡El Corazón de tu mazmorra está siendo atacado!"

#: speech:9
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your minions have lost a battle."
msgstr "Tus servidores han perdido una batalla."

#: speech:10
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures have won a battle!"
msgstr "¡Tus criaturas han ganado una batalla!"

#: speech:11
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are falling in battle!"
msgstr "¡Tus criaturas están cayendo en la batalla!"

#: speech:12
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your minions are winning a battle."
msgstr "Tus servidores están ganando una batalla."

#: speech:13
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are under attack."
msgstr "Tus criaturas están siendo atacadas."

#: speech:14
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are attacking the enemy!"
msgstr "¡Tus criaturas están atacando al enemigo!"

#: speech:15
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The enemy is destroying your rooms!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo está destruyendo tus cámaras!"

#: speech:16
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You are losing territory."
msgstr "Estás perdiendo territorio."

#: speech:17
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have claimed an enemy room."
msgstr "Has reclamado una cámara enemiga."

#: speech:18
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have taken control of a new room."
msgstr "Has tomado el control de una nueva cámara."

#: speech:19
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Beware, the lord of the land approaches!"
msgstr "Ten cuidado, ¡el señor de la tierra se aproxima!"

#: speech:20
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures are fighting amongst themselves."
msgstr "Tus criaturas están peleando entre sí."

#: speech:21
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The battle is over."
msgstr "La batalla ha terminado."

#: speech:22
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Food is scarce, enlarge your Hatchery."
msgstr "El alimento escasea, amplía tu criadero."

#: speech:23
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures need a bigger Lair."
msgstr "Tus criaturas necesitan una guarida mayor."

#: speech:24
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You need a bigger Treasure Room."
msgstr "Necesitas una cámara del tesoro mayor."

#: speech:25
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Library is too small."
msgstr "Tu biblioteca es demasiado pequeña."

#: speech:26
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Prison is too small."
msgstr "Tu prisión es demasiado pequeña."

#: speech:27
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Torture Chamber is not big enough."
msgstr "Tu cámara de torturas no es suficientemente grande."

#: speech:28
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You need a bigger Training Room."
msgstr "Necesitas una sala de entrenamiento mayor."

#: speech:29
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Workshop is not big enough."
msgstr "Tu taller no es suficientemente grande."

#: speech:30
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Scavenger Room is too small."
msgstr "Tu cámara del depredador es demasiado pequeña."

#: speech:31
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You need a bigger Temple."
msgstr "Necesitas un templo mayor."

#: speech:32
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Graveyard is not big enough."
msgstr "Tu cementerio no es suficientemente grande."

#: speech:33
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your Barracks require expansion."
msgstr "Tus barracas necesitan expansión."

#: speech:34
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Hungry creatures cannot get to a Hatchery."
msgstr "Las criaturas hambrientas no pueden llegar a un criadero."

#: speech:35
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Some of your minions are unable to reach the Treasure Room."
msgstr "Algunos de tus servidores son incapaces de llegar a la cámara del tesoro."

#: speech:36
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Some of your minions are unable to reach their lairs."
msgstr "Algunos de tus servidores son incapaces de llegar a sus guaridas."

#: speech:37
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "An Entrance has been claimed."
msgstr "Una entrada ha sido reclamada."

#: speech:38
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have lost an entrance."
msgstr "Has perdido una entrada."

#: speech:39
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You must build a Treasure Room, to store gold."
msgstr "Debes construir una cámara del tesoro para almacenar oro."

#: speech:40
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You need to build a Lair for your creatures."
msgstr "Necesitas construir una guarida para tus criaturas."

#: speech:41
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You should build a Hatchery, to feed your minions."
msgstr "Debes construir un criadero, para alimentar a tus servidores."

#: speech:42
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A new room has been researched."
msgstr "Se ha investigado una nueva cámara."

#: speech:43
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A new spell has been researched."
msgstr "Se ha investigado un nuevo conjuro."

#: speech:44
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A door has been manufactured."
msgstr "Se ha fabricado una puerta."

#: speech:45
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A trap has been manufactured."
msgstr "Se ha fabricado una trampa."

#: speech:46
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "There is nothing left to research."
msgstr "No queda nada que investigar."

#: speech:47
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have taken an enemy's spellbook."
msgstr "Has tomado un libro de conjuros del enemigo."

#: speech:48
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have taken an enemy's trap design."
msgstr "Has tomado un diseño de una trampa enemiga."

#: speech:49
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have taken an enemy's door design."
msgstr "Has tomado un diseño de una puerta enemiga."

#: speech:50
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The enemy has stolen a spellbook!"
msgstr "¡El enemigo ha robado un libro de conjuros!"

#: speech:51
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A trap design has been taken from you."
msgstr "Te han quitado un diseño de trampa."

#: speech:52
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The enemy has taken a door design."
msgstr "El enemigo ha tomado un diseño de puerta."

#: speech:53
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Information has been tortured from the enemy."
msgstr "Se ha obtenido información del enemigo bajo tortura."

#: speech:54
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "An enemy has been converted to your cause."
msgstr "Un enemigo ha sido convertido a tu causa."

#: speech:55
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A prisoner has died and risen as a Skeleton."
msgstr "Un prisionero ha muerto y se ha levantado como un esqueleto."

#: speech:56
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A torture victim has died and returned as a Ghost."
msgstr "Una víctima de torturas ha muerto y ha vuelto como un fantasma."

#: speech:57
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your prisoners are escaping!"
msgstr "¡Tus prisioneros se están escapando!"

#: speech:58
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A Vampire has risen in your Graveyard."
msgstr "Ha surgido un vampiro en tu cementerio."

#: speech:59
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have freed your creatures from prison!"
msgstr "¡Has liberado a tus criaturas de prisión!"

#: speech:60
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your prisoners are starving to death."
msgstr "Tus prisioneros se mueren de hambre."

#: speech:61
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "One of your creatures is being scavenged!"
msgstr "¡Una de tus criaturas está siendo depredada!"

#: speech:62
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "One of your minions has been scavenged!"
msgstr "¡Uno de tus servidores está siendo depredado!"

#: speech:63
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "One of your creatures has joined the enemy."
msgstr "Una de tus criaturas se ha unido al enemigo."

#: speech:64
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Secrets have been tortured from your creatures!"
msgstr "¡Se ha obtenido secretos de tus criaturas bajo torturas!"

#. Message when good sacrifice recipe progressed
#: speech:65
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The Gods are pleased with your sacrifice."
msgstr "Los dioses están satisfechos con tu sacrificio."

#. Message when good sacrifice recipe finished
#: speech:66
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The Gods have rewarded your offering."
msgstr "Los dioses han recompensado tu ofrenda."

#. Message when sacrifice didn't progressed any recipe
#: speech:67
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The Gods do not care for your sacrifice."
msgstr "A los dioses no les importa tu sacrificio."

#. Message when bad sacrifice recipe progressed
#: speech:68
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your offering has made the Gods angry!"
msgstr "¡Tu ofrenda ha irritado a los dioses!"

#. Message when bad sacrifice recipe finished
#: speech:69
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The Gods have punished your unworthy offering."
msgstr "Los dioses han castigado tu miserable ofrenda."

#. Message when dropping gold into Temple water
#: speech:70
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "This is no wishing well, keeper."
msgstr "No hay pozo de los deseos, guardián."

#. Message when Dungeon Special found on level
#: speech:71
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures have discovered a mysterious magic box."
msgstr "Tus criaturas han descubierto una misteriosa caja mágica."

#. Message when spellbook found on level
#: speech:72
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures have found a spell."
msgstr "Tus criaturas han hallado un conjuro."

#. Message when door crate found on level
#: speech:73
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A door design has been discovered."
msgstr "Ha sido descubierto un diseño de puerta."

#. Message when trap crate found on level
#: speech:74
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "A trap design has been discovered."
msgstr "Ha sido descubierto un diseño de trampa."

#: speech:75
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "New creatures have joined your dungeon."
msgstr "Nuevas criaturas se han unido a tu mazmorra."

#. Message when digging has revealed a cavern
#: speech:76
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have tunneled into a new area."
msgstr "Has pasado por un túnel a una zona nueva."

#: speech:77
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "The entire realm has been revealed to you."
msgstr "El reino entero te ha sido revelado."

#: speech:78
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You may resurrect one creature."
msgstr "Debes resucitar una criatura."

#: speech:79
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Select a creature to take with you to the next realm."
msgstr "Selecciona una criatura para llevarla contigo al siguiente reino."

#: speech:80
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "So be it."
msgstr "Así sea."

#: speech:81
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have bewitched a hero."
msgstr "Has embrujado a un héroe."

#: speech:82
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures have been doubled in number."
msgstr "El número de tus criaturas se ha duplicado."

#: speech:83
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your creatures have been blessed with experience."
msgstr "Tus criaturas han sido bendecidas con experiencia."

#: speech:84
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your dungeon has been fortified."
msgstr "Tu mazmorra ha sido fortificada."

#: speech:85
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have found a hidden realm. Go there when you've conquered this land."
msgstr "Has hallado un reino oculto. Ve allí cuando hayas conquistado esta tierra."

#: speech:86
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Your gold reserves are running low."
msgstr "Tus reservas de oro están disminuyendo."

#: speech:87
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You do not have enough gold."
msgstr "No tienes suficiente oro."

#: speech:88
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You are too poor to scavenge creatures."
msgstr "Eres demasiado pobre para encontrar criaturas."

#: speech:89
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You cannot afford to train creatures."
msgstr "No puedes permitirte entrenar criaturas."

#: speech:90
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "It is payday."
msgstr "Es día de pago."

#: speech:91
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "My god, it's full of pies."
msgstr "Dios, está lleno de pasteles."

#: speech:92
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Something surreal is happening."
msgstr "Está ocurriendo algo surrealista."

#: speech:93
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Your creatures are developing a strange accent."
msgstr "Tus criaturas están desarrollando un acento extraño."

#: speech:94
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Your pants are definitely too tight."
msgstr "Definitivamente, tus pantalones son demasiado estrechos."

#: speech:95
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Your minions have a craving for chocolate."
msgstr "Tus servidores tienen antojos de chocolate."

#: speech:96
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "There's that smell again."
msgstr "De nuevo vuelve ese olor."

#: speech:97
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Hello?"
msgstr "¿Hola?"

#: speech:98
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Blech."
msgstr "Desconvertido, vaya."

#: speech:99
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Achoo"
msgstr "Achus"

#: speech:100
msgctxt "In-game mentor random funny message"
msgid "Cough"
msgstr "Cof, cofff."

#: speech:101
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You cannot give your Imps any more jobs."
msgstr "No puedes darle más trabajo a tus duendes."

#: speech:102
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Game loaded."
msgstr "Juego cargado."

#: speech:103
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Game saved."
msgstr "Juego salvado."

#: speech:104
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have defeated an enemy Keeper."
msgstr "Has derrotado a un guardián enemigo."

#: speech:105
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have been defeated."
msgstr "Has sido derrotado."

#: speech:106
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You have conquered this realm!"
msgstr "¡Has conquistado este reino!"

#: speech:107
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "Master, I sense the presence of the Avatar!"
msgstr "¡Amo, percibo la presencia del Avatar!"

#: speech:108
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "What trickery is this? The Avatar's body has vanished."
msgstr "¿Qué truco es este? El cuerpo del Avatar ha desaparecido."

#: speech:109
msgctxt "In-game mentor"
msgid "You are victorious, your darkness pervades throughout the kingdom. All hail the new lord of shadows."
msgstr "Has vencido, tu oscuridad se extiende por el reino. Viva el nuevo señor de las sombras."

#: speech:110
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "Your efforts are futile!"
msgstr "¡Tus esfuerzos son inútiles!"

#: speech:111
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "My dungeon is the finest you shall ever see!"
msgstr "¡Mi mazmorra es la mejor que verás en toda tu vida!"

#: speech:112
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "My minions will leave your dungeon a crumbling ruin!"
msgstr "¡Mis servidores dejarán tu mazmorra, echa una ruina!"

#: speech:113
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "You entrails will decorate the darkest alchove of my domain!"
msgstr "¡Tus entrañas decorarán la alcoba más oscura de mi dominio!"

#: speech:114
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "Your corpse shall feed my minions yet, keeper!"
msgstr "¡Tu cadáver aún alimentará a mis servidores, guardián!"

#: speech:115
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "Prepare for oblivion, Keeper!"
msgstr "¡Prepárate para la nada, guardián!"

#: speech:116
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "Pathetic creature, I shall crush you in an instant!"
msgstr "¡Criatura patética, te aplastaré en un instante!"

#: speech:117
msgctxt "Enemy Keeper Harassment"
msgid "Ho ho ho ho!"
msgstr "¡Ha ha ha ha!"

#: speech:118
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "Your dark days are numbered, evil one!"
msgstr "¡Tus negros días están contados, maligno!"

#: speech:119
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "We come to rid the world of your evil!"
msgstr "¡Hemos venido a eliminar tu maldad del mundo!"

#: speech:120
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "We shall send you back to the pits, vile one!"
msgstr "¡Te enviaremos de vuelta al agujero, malvado!"

#: speech:121
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "Your reign shall end before this day is done!"
msgstr "¡Tu reinado terminará antes que concluya el día!"

#: speech:122
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "We shall cast you back into the shadows, keeper!"
msgstr "¡Te haremos retornar a las tinieblas, guardián!"

#: speech:123
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "Leave us to live our lives in peace!"
msgstr "¡Deja que vivamos nuestras vidas en paz!"

#: speech:124
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "In the name of all that is good, we shall defeat you!"
msgstr "¡Te derrotaremos, en nombre de todo lo que es bueno!"

#: speech:125
msgctxt "Hero Talk Upon Entering"
msgid "We shall not tolerate your evil presence any longer!"
msgstr "¡No toleraremos más tu presencia malvada!"
